headline: Tradr Rolls Out Short Leveraged ETFs on APLD, IREN, LCID & NBIS
summary: Tradr ETFs, a provider of ETFs designed for sophisticated investors and professional traders, today launched four new short leveraged ETFs on single stocks. The Cboe-listed funds seek to deliver the inverse of twice (-200%) the daily performance of a specific underlying stock.
